[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1443[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the assistant cannot detect the gaps that are its distinctive value, the protocol-driven engagement cadence is missing, the care-team feedback loop is broken, and the assistant degrades to a glorified FAQ bot over coordination data. The seam-detection-rule library and the protocol library together are the largest non-LLM engineering investment in the system.
